title: Episode 159: Scot McKay - 100+ Countries With The Wife & Kids
description:
Scot McKay is one of the "OG" dating coaches who gained massive popularity back in 2007 as the only married coach. He has travelled to 100+ countries, most of them with his wife and kids which is truly remarkable. He is also the host of The Mountain Top Podcast from X & Y Communications - the definitive podcast for evolved men of character. Scot and his expert co-hosts talk women, dating, relationships, sex, and 21st century masculinity in a fast-paced, entertaining and often controversial style. 

Show Notes:

When is the “time to get married?”
The number one personality trait to avoid in women and the dangerous V-word…
Are women attracted to men for the same reasons men are attracted to women?
The two best Hollywood characters that embody the most attractive archetype of a man…
What to avoid doing to make sure women feel safe in you presence…
The key to staying content in a monogamous long term relationship…
Deserving what you want…
How to be a digital nomad with a family…
Scot’s surprising visit to Moscow during the Soviet period…
How to “World School” your children…
Scot’s favorite countries on each continent…
Can you wing-it when traveling with your family? How much preparation is required?
The best kept secret city of Eastern Europe…
